{"tid":1207483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果雨革再黎一次你會點做？","createTime":"2019-06-12T06:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T06:46:19.000Z","uid":64181,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d94d5c0d77de36df7fe08ca96f5273572c215e5f","tid":1207483,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:39:48.000Z","msg":"依家就同果陣一鳩樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/62320179_2255674961136196_3781770432714113024_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=d71adfa54a72ab71e3042a74fc61cb4e&amp;oe=5D865037\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F62320179_2255674961136196_3781770432714113024_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3Dd71adfa54a72ab71e3042a74fc61cb4e%26oe%3D5D865037&h=1da1e88d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆 大台 wtsapp fake news 全部膠野一撚樣，根本同我地全部時光倒流返去2014一樣，當然對面嘅黑暗同武力比以前更勁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/030900_64bd136839e8e2ceef4e099ca493c8af.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F030900_64bd136839e8e2ceef4e099ca493c8af.gif&h=80c5e093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果我地好似睇咗預言書咁都係人類總要重複同樣的錯誤，咁不如算啦，個結局大家都知會點<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/16/Repetitive_error.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20070902105305\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F16%2FRepetitive_error.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070902105305&h=b7a3ba40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有雖然鄺標點同班吟遊詩人尋晚幫到手，但假若佢地之後叫大家和理非/用歌聲感動人地，大家都應該是其是屌佢地，而唔係因為幫過一次就比佢地之後做膠野"},{"pid":"841728c14e87b4cb23da83fec7629a81263d72a9","tid":1207483,"uid":148067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:40:20.000Z","msg":"[想衝但又怕嘅入嚟] 各種分工 衝要用腦有陣形<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1200053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1200053</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35c23f3cbae08bd50155d6180d6f2e439300f749","tid":1207483,"uid":163758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:40:44.000Z","msg":"龍鼓灘"},{"pid":"ec94115a2cc308fd4e0193f8e6256fa0de74cf5f","tid":1207483,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:41:22.000Z","msg":"2014已經令義士失望一次，今次多返咁多，唔好再令佢地失望多次"},{"pid":"3f3b006e521ab0cbfa640d2c1f237e0f181a5c85","tid":1207483,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:41:32.000Z","msg":"有人用棍拍野deam beat 既時候唔好劣<br />\n一齊叫同一句口號加士氣避免士氣此消彼長<br />\n有心理學背後原理<br />\n對陣口號<br />\n拍拍~拍拍拍~DIE FOR HONG KONG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家小心雙眼，戴眼罩被人噴油漆就喪失視力，唔戴又會比人插眼<br />\n<br />\n大家亦小心近距離突然由下巴向上大力推有機會導致頸椎受傷 請各位注意安全免生危險<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n希望無論大家去邊，甚至返工，不了<br />\n都想大家連日常生活都黑衫黑褲口罩笠帽加黑鞋<br />\n令到平時條街見到全黑既人唔再係特徵反而係大多數<br />\n最好個個用現金，咁買飛個個就唔係做突出個一個<br />\n<br />\n全民 BLACK BLOCK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cf58c57f0016a8b677dd9ebc92ab24a839722af1","tid":1207483,"uid":207402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:42:17.000Z","msg":"絕對認同 今次對抗既係最撚黑暗既黑警同埋最撚黑心既林鄭"},{"pid":"9b6c1e224fd2af4f5cfbeb4a903b992a24dd65c3","tid":1207483,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"[想衝但又怕嘅入嚟] 各種分工 衝要用腦有陣形<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cKPROT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cKPROT</a>"},{"pid":"304709b3f132430e22a1039d66adbaeee929ebdb","tid":1207483,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:46:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要贏！</span></strong>"}]}